---
import SocialList from "@/components/SocialList.astro";
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description:
		"Manas Ganti — research engineer working on reinforcement learning, post-training, and production ML systems.",
	title: "About",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<h1 class="title mb-12">About</h1>
	<div class="prose prose-sm prose-cactus max-w-none">
		<p>
			I'm Manas Ganti, a machine learning engineer who builds computer vision and deep learning
			systems that hold up in the real world on factory floors, edge devices, and clinical imaging
			pipelines.
		</p>

		<p>
			Over the past three years I've taken models the full distance from training to production. At
			Assert AI, I built real-time computer vision pipelines on NVIDIA Jetson hardware for
			industrial safety pose estimation, PPE compliance, and automatic number-plate recognition
			running under tight latency and memory constraints across multi-camera deployments. Before
			that, at Inmed Prognostics, I developed segmentation and detection models for brain CT and MRI
			modalities, and managed engineering teams to ship them into production medical imaging
			systems.
		</p>

		<p>
			More recently my work has moved toward the multimodal and generative frontier: fine-tuning
			vision-language models, building RAG pipelines, and evaluating LLMs on real tasks. I'm
			currently pursuing an M.S. in Computer Engineering at Virginia Tech, focused on advanced
			machine learning, computer vision, and reinforcement learning.
		</p>

		<p>
			I'm deliberately pivoting toward reinforcement learning; specifically the design of RL
			environments and verifiable reward systems for training capable models. It's where my instinct
			for real-world constraints and my interest in how models actually learn come together, and
			it's the direction I'm building toward through my current projects and coursework.
		</p>

		<h2>Resume</h2>
		<p>
			<a class="cactus-link" href="/Manas-Ganti-Resume.pdf" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank">
				Résumé (PDF)
			</a>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="mt-8">
		<SocialList />
	</div>
</PageLayout>
